      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals below 1e-5 for continuity and momentum equations. Required level 1 only at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error requires only level 1 demonstration. Residual monitoring confirmed convergence to 1e-4 for all simulations; factor not formally assessed beyond this threshold per MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
