      "acceptanceCriteria": "Analyst qualifications and simulation setup review documented. Required level 1 at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 requires only level 1 for use error. Lead analyst holds PhD in computational fluid dynamics with 8 years CFD experience in cardiovascular applications. Peer review of simulation setup performed internally. Formal use-error assessment not required at this MRL."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
